to meet them.

09:39.578 --> 09:41.247
You have a boat, huh?

09:41.247 --> 09:42.665
Yes, come down.

09:42.665 --> 09:44.292
Come see the boat.

09:44.292 --> 09:46.043
We'll save you two chairs.

09:47.169 --> 09:49.046
